    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required level for MRL 2. The observational clinical registry dataset provides extensive coverage of the COU operating envelope (312 pump-hours, five operating points) and yields RH agreement within ±12%, satisfying the RH < 1 acceptance criterion. The six non-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40 Table 1. The CFD model is accepted as sufficiently credible to support identification of worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
